-	// Overlay is the name of the JSON overlay file that describes
-	// unsaved editor buffers; see [WriteOverlays].
-	// If set, the go command is invoked with -overlay=Overlay.
-	// TODO(rfindley): remove, in favor of Args.
-	Overlay string
